Title: Absent Errand
Description:
Do you remember the logbook you discovered in Zev'kall's office? It contained critical information about Zev'kall's misuse of our people. I gave it to my assistant, Anub'okki, to bring to the historians in the Skeins.

But I have not heard back from Anub'okki. I suspect foul play. See if anyone in the Skeins will admit to having seen him!
ObjectivesText: Seek out Anub'azal's student in the Skeins of Nerub'ar.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Speak to Ukos'via in the Skeins
